* 2011年4月12日 二期遺留站济阳路站启用，调整小交路为市光路站至济阳路站<ref>{{cite web | title = 4月12日起6、8号线济阳路站投入运营 实现方便换乘 | publisher = 上海地铁 | date = 2011-04-10 | url = http://www.shmetro.com/node49/201104/con107637.htm | accessdate = 2010-04-10 | language = zh | archive-date = 2011-04-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110415060359/http://www.shmetro.com/node49/201104/con107637.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>
